{"tid":2367107,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"七旬翁損毀鄭麗琼議辦海報獲撤控 准簽保守行為賠償兩元了事","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T06:45:22.000Z","uid":290870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"901644721dfa2a344674b5695bef44334d4811f7","tid":2367107,"uid":290870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"七旬翁去年6月途經中西區區議會主席鄭麗琼辦事處，用傘篤兩張印有「毋忘六四」及「無懼打壓」字句的海報，被控一項刑事損毀罪。案件今早再訊，控方同意撤銷控罪，讓涉事老翁以2,000元簽保守行為18個月結案，並賠償2元了事。<br />\n<br />\n2蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如留番俾廢老執藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n七旬翁損毀鄭麗琼議辦海報獲撤控 准簽保守行為賠償兩元了事<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/TEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FTEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFn%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=ac43006c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FTEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E%2F&h=a42fb025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/TEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E/</a>"},{"pid":"a723d6d58f2177867385de587588e5a9c8e9f7d0","tid":2367107,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"藍屍做乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0bb480e8f064b38ecf776fc987a7929edd0198","tid":2367107,"uid":370971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得保守行為係合理嘅<br />\n但係賠兩蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印過一張坐低100啦"}]}